<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="331" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="0.[831,1436,1765,1922]" pageId="0" pageNumber="331">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[831,952,1765,1788]" pageId="0" pageNumber="331">Diagnosis:</emphasis>
The new species is characterized by an essentially unmodified carapace, by the shape of the dorsal apophysis of the palpal tibia, as well as by a relatively large, cylindrical radix and by a very short embolus.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
